snippet.title: The Graham Stephan Show
snippet.description: Lets talk about more money, business, and finance related topics without worrying about the YouTube algorithm. This channel is meant to be a place where I can upload other random topics that come up, start discussions, and post freely/whenever as things come up. If that sounds good to you, subscribe!
